Package: warphud
Title: Warp ggplot2 and gt Objects for HUD-Style Image Overlays
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Luis", "D", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "luisd@example.com")
Description: Renders ggplot2 and gt objects as images, applies optional
    perspective warp distortions, and composites them over background
    images with transparency — producing a heads-up display (HUD) effect.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    magick,
    ragg,
    rlang
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    gt,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
